OL,3,CFeargal Sharkey criticises South West
OL,4,CWater for sewage spills
OL,6,FIn a statement in response South West
OL,7,FWater said: "We care about our 860
OL,8,Fmiles of coastline, our region's 100%
OL,9,Fbathing water quality, which we have
OL,10,Fsuccessfully maintained for three
OL,11,Fconsecutive years, and protecting the
OL,12,Fenvironment now and in the future.
OL,14,F"We were one of the first water
OL,15,Fcompanies to have all our storm
OL,16,Foverflows monitored meaning we know
OL,17,Fexactly what is happening, when and
OL,18,Fwhere, allowing us to target
OL,19,Finvestment and make changes where it
OL,20,Fmatters most.
