OL,6,F"We are serious about tackling storm
OL,7,Foverflows and change of this scale
OL,8,Ftakes time, ambition, and increased
OL,9,Finvestment ` and that is why we are
OL,10,Finvesting #850m in our region over two
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"The increase in the storm overflow
OL,14,Fspills this year can be accounted for
OL,15,Fby the amount of named storms and
OL,16,Fweather warnings in 2023. It's clear
OL,17,Fwe need to redesign our systems, which
